item.title: Sabrina add a quote by Kate Klise
item.description: "some wishes come true. some wishes dont. sometimes you find out you were wishing for the completely wrong thing." -- Kate Klise

item.title: Sabrina add a quote by from an inscription on cellar walls in cologne, germany
item.description: "i believe in the sun, even when it is not shining. and i believe in love, even when there's no one there. and i believe in God, even when he is silent. i believe through any trial, there is always a way." -- from an inscription on cellar walls in cologne, germany

item.title: Sabrina add a quote by Miss Piggy
item.description: "Beauty is in the eye of the beholder and it may be necessary from time to time to give a stupid or misinformed beholder a black eye." -- Miss Piggy

item.title: Sabrina add a quote by Seán O'Casey
item.description: "All the world's a stage and most of us are desperately unrehearsed." -- Seán O'Casey
